-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/goffer-sentenced-to-10-years-in-prison-for-insider-trading.html
Zvi Goffer, the ex-Galleon Group
LLC trader, was sentenced to 10 years in prison for his role in
a scheme to trade on inside information provided by lawyers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
